26:
A-Alk! Please! I'm trying to stay
hidden here!
33:
Don't tell me you're slacking off
again.
36: Ah, Ms. Orvelle! I found you!
43:
As promised, all you hide-and-seek
winners get some candy.
53:
That's right. I've been playing a lot of
games with the kids around here
lately, and we've been betting on
candy.
57:
It's been a lot of fun, and we're all
good friends now!
60:
Heh-heh! If it weren't for us, you
would have been caught for doing
the ol' dine and dash!
64:
H-hey! I told you to keep that a
secret!
72:
Y-you've got it all wrong! I was just
out for a bite to eat as usual when I
realized that I forgot my wallet!
75:
She looked SUPER sad, so we had no
choice but to pool our money
together and help her out!
78:
It would be a disaster if the church
heard about this...
82:
Do you play with these kids often,
Orvelle?
90:
It's the new year and I happened to
have a little extra money on-hand,
so this is just a special occasion.
93:
I'm not given much money to spend
on myself, after all.
96:
*sigh* It would be nice if we could
get some major reforms and
support systems in place...
100:
...So basically, you made a personal
donation under the guise of a
friendly competition?
104: You just figured it out, huh?
107:
Alk. Surely you didn't think I was
actually just gambling away candy
with some kids?
118:
Well, whatever... It's true that I've
been enjoying myself.
122:
...Right now, this is about the limit of
what I can do to help others.
127:
You said something about this once,
didn't you? About being a
figurehead, shining as a beacon for
all people, equally.
131:
Yes. My position does not allow me
to reach out to specific individuals.
138:
That's why, recently, I've been
thinking...
141:
Things would be a whole lot easier if
I abandoned just a few of these
annoying restrictions.
144: Not that I'm actually going to.
159:
Lady Stella, you and Alk decided
that you'll fight those winged
creatures, correct?
164:
...Well, probably, yeah. Would it be
wrong for you to fight them?
168:
No. My prayers are not directed at
those beings.
172:
And... I've decided that I want to
fight, too.
175:
Lady Stella! I'm starting to feel
excited!
184:
Hey, Ms. Orvelle! Did you really do
the New Year's prayers in that outfit?
187: I sure did. A whole ton of them, too!
191:
Come to think of it, this would be a
perfect opportunity to pray a
blessing on you all!
194:
O Stars, bless all your children, no
matter where they be.
197: Together, we pray for your guidance!
203: Heh! What do you say to that?
207: I'm a pretty splendid saint, aren't I?
211:
Yeah, but... Are you sure that was a
good idea?
215:
To bless them? I'm not supposed to,
but I've made up my mind! Today's
the day I start kicking aside
needless restrictions!
224:
That light! Lady Orvelle must be
slacking off somewhere in that
direction! Find her!
228: Oh, come ON. I completely forgot!
232: Let's go, you three! We need to run!
236:
And let me hide out with you for one
more day!
